This well presented stand alone unit is on the top of Buderim.

If you want to do without the car and walk to local shops, restaurants/cafes and supermarket, or catch a bus – these amenities are a short stroll. 

The unit complex is not a retirement village.

This property comes with the following qualities – 

•Freehold 2 bedroom single storey unit; 
•Low body corporate fees; 
•Single lock up garage; 
•Solar panels – made in Germany (no current electricity bills); 
•Good quality roof insulation;
•Reverse cycle heating / cooling (but given insulation and cross breezes through unit, the heating/cooling is rarely required – giving savings to electricity); 
•1 bathroom (with double sized shower); 1 toilet;
•Built in robes in bedrooms;
•Private rear corner yard – a good place to sit and relax; 
•Existing and productive vegetable garden which is aesthetically pleasing with herbs, vegetables, shrubs & trees. This garden is easily maintained and the size of the garden does not it make a slave to the owner; 
•Light and airy, with views of garden from each window;
•4 burner gas stove; 
•Electric hot water system;
•New floor coverings in living area;
•Short stroll to bus stop, restaurants, cafés, supermarket and shops in Buderim;
•Bus stop out front of complex.

